@page "/about"
@layout MainLayout

<PageTitle>About | SPC Technology</PageTitle>

<section class="section">
    <div class="container">
        <p class="eyebrow">About SPC Technology</p>
        <h1>About</h1>
        <p class="lead">
            SPC Technology is a turnkey software and business solution provider established in 2004 to help customers move into the next generation of business innovation through software, automation, and consulting.
        </p>
        <p>
            The company focuses on delivering business solutions that bridge the gap between business operations and technology. Its experience includes finance and accounting, human resources, hospitality, property management, and freight forwarding systems.
        </p>
        <p>
            For businesses operating in the information age, SPC Technology helps organizations use technology as a practical advantage through software development, implementation, and consultation services.
        </p>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="section section--alt">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="section-shell">
            <div class="section-header">
                <h2 class="section-title">Who We Are</h2>
                <p class="section-intro">
                    SPC Technology delivers high-value software solutions by combining product development, business process understanding, and implementation capability.
                </p>
            </div>
            <p>
                Since 2004, the company has been helping businesses improve operations with software that supports automation, structured processes, and operational visibility. This experience continues today through Phoebus ERP and the services built around it.
            </p>
            <ul>
                <li>Established in 2004</li>
                <li>500+ clients worldwide</li>
                <li>217+ projects completed</li>
                <li>30+ team members</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="section-shell">
            <div class="section-header">
                <h2 class="section-title">Our Mission</h2>
                <p class="section-intro">
                    Empowering client success, fostering growth, and enriching communities.
                </p>
            </div>
            <p>
                The company mission is reflected in the way SPC Technology approaches client delivery: practical solutions, long-term support, and software that helps customers improve business operations in measurable ways.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="section section--alt">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="section-shell">
            <div class="section-header">
                <h2 class="section-title">Consulting Team Leaders</h2>
                <p class="section-intro">
                    Bridging technology and business through implementation, consulting, and operational understanding.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="team-grid">
                <article class="team-member">
                    <img src="/images/team/thanhthuan.jpg" alt="Phan Thi Thanh Thuan" class="team-member__photo" />
                    <h3>Phan Thi Thanh Thuan</h3>
                    <p class="team-member__role">Executive Director and leader of the Consulting Team</p>
                    <p>
                        Phan Thi Thanh Thuan leads the Consulting Team with a strong background in consulting and operations management.
                        She is known for delivering customized solutions and driving digital transformation for businesses of different sizes.
                    </p>
                </article>

                <article class="team-member">
                    <img src="/images/team/daovuong.jpg" alt="Vuong Cam Dao" class="team-member__photo" />
                    <h3>Vuong Cam Dao</h3>
                    <p class="team-member__role">Consultant</p>
                    <p>
                        Vuong Cam Dao is an experienced consultant trusted for successful implementations across industries.
                        Her strengths include project management, process improvement, and software implementation.
                    </p>
                </article>

                <article class="team-member">
                    <img src="/images/team/thanhtin.jpg" alt="Vo Thanh Tin" class="team-member__photo" />
                    <h3>Vo Thanh Tin</h3>
                    <p class="team-member__role">Consultant</p>
                    <p>
                        Vo Thanh Tin is a senior software consultant with a strong academic background in Information Systems.
                        He brings extensive experience in accounting and real estate operation systems.
                    </p>
                </article>

                <article class="team-member">
                    <div class="team-member__photo team-member__photo--placeholder" aria-hidden="true">SPC</div>
                    <h3>Nguyen Tan Phat</h3>
                    <p class="team-member__role">Consultant</p>
                    <p>
                        Nguyen Tan Phat is recognized for productivity, creative thinking, and prompt delivery.
                        His ability to approach problems from fresh perspectives makes him a strong contributor to the consulting team.
                    </p>
                </article>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="section-shell">
            <div class="section-header">
                <h2 class="section-title">Development Leaders</h2>
