                    <p class="team-member__role">Director and Software Architect</p>
                    <p>
                        Ngo Thanh Tung is an experienced professional in economics and software architecture with more than a decade of experience delivering innovative solutions to businesses.
                        As founder of the organization, he has played a major role in building a culture of excellence, innovation, and client satisfaction.
                    </p>
                </article>

                <article class="team-member">
                    <div class="team-member__photo team-member__photo--placeholder" aria-hidden="true">SPC</div>
                    <h3>Vo Hoang Quan</h3>
